Text: Well it got a 4.1 out of 10

Thanks for sharing.  In downloading it is always good to get A/V quality reports which are pretty reliable.  Scene4all has a good reputation for quality anyway.

Whether or not someone actually likes it, is completely a matter of taste.  I've hated some that are highly rated and loved others that were poorly rated.  I suppose there are some people who need to be told what is good rather than deciding for themselves.
